Today I solved the following LeetCode problem in Python:

## âœ… 520. Detect Capital  
**Problem Link:** [Detect Capital](https://leetcode.com/problems/detect-capital/)  
**Approach:** Used Python string methods (`isupper`, `islower`, and slicing) to validate the usage of capital letters in different cases.

```python
class Solution(object):
    def detectCapitalUse(self, word):
        """
        :type word: str
        :rtype: bool
        """
        if word.isupper():
            return True
        if word.islower():
            return True
        if word[0].isupper() and word[1:].islower():
            return True
        return False
```

